<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/441832-625x402.jpg" alt="Purity Cereals gets new look" width="625" height="402">Berge Farrell’s task was to revitalise the cereal packaging and roll it out across the extensive range. This trusted range caters and supports parents in their child’s journey of growth through varying age development stages.Purity baby food has always stood for “Quality food, made with love”, and the packs are designed to showcase their nutritional benefits created with South African babies and toddlers in mind.